cause_of_action: negligence by customs officers causing damage to imported goods
procedure_followed: Defendants moved for summary judgment and removal from simplified action rules. Federal Court reviewed limitation periods and causation.
decision_reasoning: Plaintiff became aware of damage by October 5, 2009, but filed the claim on September 20, 2011, exceeding the limitation period. No evidence supported a claim against the Minister of National Revenue.
result_of_case: Action dismissed with costs to defendants; motion for summary judgment granted.
